name: D'Crossier - Presidential Collection - Taino
additionalNotes: The Presidential Collection began as the Presidential Four Pack in the Diplomacy Series.  This new line of cigars is handcrafted in San Jose, Costa Rica, using a beautiful Habano Criollo Especial wrapper, a Habano binder with fillers from Brazil and the Dominican Republic. The cigar is medium to full body with a full range of flavors and has been aging in Santana’s Humidor for approximately 19 months. The wrapper is from Costa Rica with Ecuadorean binder and Dominican Republic fillers along with it being a medium to full strength.
